{"tid":1560704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你無攬炒既勇氣 你無抗爭既資格","createTime":"2019-09-11T10:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T03:03:24.000Z","uid":61886,"like":60,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e93cf677826fff8e5b9465e0ab8a1d27367ea1c0","tid":1560704,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:12:42.000Z","msg":"我地而家就好似同中共玩poker<br />\n攬炒就好似all in<br />\n我地唔怕攬炒 因為<br />\n7成外資由香港入中國<br />\n香港係中共既白手套<br />\n香港係中美貿易戰既春袋<br />\n中共係唔敢同香港攬炒<br />\n情況同 解放軍 緊急法 一樣<br />\n<br />\n如果攬炒發生 結果會係<br />\n中共係會同香港一齊攬炒<br />\n攬炒完 可能我地會變成新疆<br />\n香港人喺依一代之後消失<br />\n<br />\n但消滅到中共政權<br />\n我地都值得記載喺歷史書<br />\n<br />\n但如果當你好驚攬炒 <br />\n(利申 供緊樓 最多咪變銀主盤)<br />\n中共亦知你好驚攬炒<br />\n等同poker開左底牌同中共玩<br />\n係必敗無疑<br />\n<br />\n攬炒係手段 亦可能係結果<br />\n無人知道結局會係點<br />\n可能真係大家攬炒<br />\n中共倒台 香港玩完<br />\n<br />\n但我深信<br />\n依個抗爭既時機同機遇<br />\n係百年難得一見<br />\n如果你無放手攬炒既勇氣<br />\n我地只會失敗收場<br />\n<br />\nIf we burn, you burn with us!"},{"pid":"50be6485db6753232c66eaf75554fec1027391cc","tid":1560704,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:13:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"7e680202157bebe48c7858a47b2a36a33fc0a616","tid":1560704,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi